# Smart Packing - React Native Project Structure

## Project Overview
This is a React Native application built with Expo that supports Android, iOS, and Web platforms. The app uses Expo Router for navigation and follows a modern React Native architecture.

## Key Files and Directories

### Core Configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Main project configuration and dependencies
- [app.json](mdc:app.json) - Expo configuration with platform-specific settings
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration with path aliases
- [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js) - ESLint configuration for code quality

### Application Structure
- [app/](mdc:app/) - Main application directory using Expo Router
  - [_layout.tsx](mdc:app/_layout.tsx) - Root layout component
  - [(tabs)/](mdc:app/(tabs)/) - Tab-based navigation structure
  - [+not-found.tsx](mdc:app/+not-found.tsx) - 404 error page

### Components and UI
- [components/](mdc:components/) - Reusable React components
  - [ui/](mdc:components/ui/) - UI-specific components
  - [ThemedText.tsx](mdc:components/ThemedText.tsx) - Themed text component
  - [ThemedView.tsx](mdc:components/ThemedView.tsx) - Themed view component
  - [Collapsible.tsx](mdc:components/Collapsible.tsx) - Collapsible content component

### Styling and Theming
- [constants/Colors.ts](mdc:constants/Colors.ts) - Color definitions and theme constants
- [hooks/useColorScheme.ts](mdc:hooks/useColorScheme.ts) - Color scheme hook
- [hooks/useThemeColor.ts](mdc:hooks/useThemeColor.ts) - Theme color utilities

### Assets
- [assets/](mdc:assets/) - Static assets including images and icons

## Platform Support
- **Android**: Native Android support with adaptive icons
- **iOS**: Native iOS support with SwiftUI integration capability
- **Web**: Web platform support with static output

## Key Technologies
- React Native 0.79.5
- Expo SDK 53
- TypeScript for type safety
- Expo Router for navigation
- React Navigation for tab navigation
